snippet: Rafael Nadal won his first match of the new season 6-7 (5) 6-3, 6-1 against Spanish countryman Pablo Carreno at the Qatar Open on Tuesday....
lead_paragraph: Rafael Nadal won his first match of the new season 6-7 (5) 6-3, 6-1 against Spanish countryman Pablo Carreno at the Qatar Open on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Nadal Wins First Match of 2016 at Qatar Open
headline.main: Nadal Wins First Match of 2016 at Qatar Open
